{"tid":2056312,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"全球新型肺炎病例突破700萬宗 新西蘭解除社交限制","createTime":"2020-06-08T14:50:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-08T14:53:43.000Z","uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7c56c4c38da9f500ac675b973e704d69377ecabd","tid":2056312,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:50:37.000Z","msg":"全球新型肺炎病例突破700萬宗 新西蘭解除社交限制<br />\n2020-06-08 HKT 21:35<br />\n<br />\n全球的新型肺炎確診個案突破700萬宗，超過40萬人死亡；其中美國、巴西和印度，單日新增個案仍然有過萬宗。<br />\n<br />\n部分國家疫情進一步緩和。其中新西蘭星期二起，把全國警戒級別降至最低的第一級，並解除保持社交距離的規定。在日本，因為疫情關閉約三個月的大阪環球影城局部重開。<br />\n<br />\n歐洲方面，英國星期一起規定所有入境人士自我隔離兩星期，並要申報住址以便當局抽查；西班牙馬德里的酒吧餐廳恢復正常營業，兒童外出活動的限制亦取消。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530903-20200608.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530903-20200608.htm&d=N73AYdKZ8ITSJgwUZ5%2B19jbTr8NPmLdj%2FTsGYWOA6so%3D&h=ec43a47a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1530903-20200608.htm&h=34f189f9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1530903-20200608.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港何時才能解除社交限制的規定</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span>"},{"pid":"4e0a90a01a4a40741147f74d43f94abee15f7367","tid":2056312,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-08T14:53:43.000Z","msg":"係唔比遊行集會姐"}]}